review_blob: Nice horsey Brett nose. Great head and lacing, perfect darker golden hue. taste is more funk and fruit than horse. Nicely crisp. Hides its 8% well.
A wonderful full bodied stout with chocolate, coffee, and nice rounded mineral flavor. Hops and sweetness finish it out perfectly.
beer_name: De Molen / Struise Brouwers Black Damnation
